# CREATING BY ATTACHING ROLE / POLICY / PERMISSION

policyid, permissionid and roleid are optional arguments you can pass to the respective methods to create by attaching policy, permission and role respectively.

``` javascript

const roleWithPolicy = await role.create({ 
 name: "SE",
 policyid: ["1", "2"]
})

const permissionWithPolicy = await permission.create({
  resource: "task",
  action: "read",
  permissionid: ["1", "2"]
});

const policyWithPermission = await policy.createWithAllowOrDeny({
  name: "task-author",
  kind: "ALLOW",
  permissionid: ["1", "2"]
});

```